### Arabic

قَالَا رَبَّنَآ إِنَّنَا نَخَافُ أَن يَفْرُطَ عَلَيْنَآ أَوْ أَن يَطْغَىٰ

### English

They both pleaded, “Our Lord! We fear that he may be quick to harm us or act tyrannically.”